  "name": "RPlog_Corellian_Craziness",
  "title": "Corellian Craziness",
  "summary": "At Coronet spaceport, the wandering trio of the cloaked girl Mira, the alien lightstaff-bearer Simon, and the white-haired Corellian Markus Lisardis prepare to leave when New Republic Intelligence officer Bazil McKenzie, intrigued by Simon's weapon and their questions about Luke Skywalker, strikes up a wary conversation. Their parley is shattered when a disguised driver guns down a protocol droid and kidnaps Kathryn, the human wife of the Calibop Senator Jrevelian, sparking a frantic aerial chase. Markus commandeers Bazil's armored hoverlimo while Simon leaps out and uses the Force to slice open the speeding sedan and pull Kathryn to safety, both crashing hard to the pavement. The kidnapper's sedan explodes, the limo crashes and is destroyed, and everyone is left battered with cracked ribs but alive. Bazil, sick of his perilous job, promises to take the trio to meet Skywalker once the medics clear them.",
